Terminal multiplexer (like screen)

start new with session name:

    tmux
    
attach:

    tmux a
    tmux attach
    tmux a -t session_id

list sessions:

    tmux ls

kill session:

    tmux kill-session -t session_id

Detach from the current session:

    Ctrl-b + d

## Windows/Panes

Split window:

    C-b %    # Split vertically
    C-b "    # Split horizontally

Resize pane:

    C-b Ctrl-arrow   # Keep Ctrl pressed
    C-b Alt-arrow    # Same as Ctrl but faster

Scroll:

    C-b Page-Up
    C-b Page-Down

